<h3 id="750">3.1. Creating content of the type “Item view”</h3>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CMS » ShopBuilder</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on a grey item category on the left.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-plus  "></i></span> <strong>Add content</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the type <strong>Item view</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a name and choose a preset if desired.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click <strong>Create</strong>.<br>
→ The new content is displayed in the overview.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="imageblock">
<div class="content">
<img src="{{plugin_path('PlentyManual')}}/images/item/online-store/assets/cross-selling-content.gif" alt="cross selling content">
