<p>Add the widget <strong>Item » Item list</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-cog  "></i></span> for the widget.<br>
→ The widget settings are displayed on the right.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Specify that the widget should be a cross-selling list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="psicon-save"></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
