<h2 id="950">4. FAQ</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="openblock collapseBox">
<div class="title"><strong>My cross-selling item isn’t displayed in the plentyShop. Why?</strong></div>
<div class="content">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The following requirements have to be met in order for direct cross-selling items to be displayed in the plentyShop:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/online-store/checklist-categories-visibility">The cross-selling item’s category must be activated</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/online-store/checklist-items-visibility">The items must be visible in the plentyShop</a>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
